# JBD2 Phase 1 candidate list
# Goal: validate block-level JBD2 (ordered mode) implementation on top of phase6 scope:
# journal replay on clean/dirty umount, orphan recovery, metadata checksum,
# ext4-specific journal recovery scripts.
#
# Tests that depend on dm-log-writes / dm-flakey are listed in
# blocked/jbd_phase1_excluded.tsv with rationale — Asterinas currently has no
# device-mapper support, and those tests will be reintroduced once dm infra lands
# (or replaced with custom ext4_crash scenarios in run_ext4_crash_test.sh).

